The paper discusses the security analysis of mobile D2D file sharing applications, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also discusses the use of Wi-Fi Direct, which is a networking protocol and falls under the category of computer networks (cs.NI). The paper also discusses the usability and design of such applications, which falls under the category of software engineering (cs.SE). The paper also mentions the use of mobile devices and cameras, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of IoT devices, which falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
